                <h1>Essential Tips for Passport Photo Outfits</h1>
                <p>When preparing for a passport photo, opt for solid colors that contrast with the background. Avoid busy patterns and bright colors. A collared shirt or blouse is ideal, and ensure your outfit is modest and reflects your personal style. Keep accessories minimal to maintain focus on your face. Good grooming is essential!</p>
